title: Strange Ideas \& Impure Thoughts Journal
description:
This journal will make you the envy of the coffee shop with its faux vintage cover and eye-catching gold lettering. Perfect for writing, drawing, or visual thinking of all types. Binding lies flat when open, and it's the perfect size for a purse or for traveling.
  • Dimensions: 5 x 7 in.
  • Materials: Stylish gold foil stamped cover, 80lb. woodfree paper, 120 gsm creamy off-white paper
  • Pages: 120 dotted
